{
  "video_id": "rThUrXYaneo",
  "title": "How I help free innocent people from prison | Ronald Sullivan",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12510.0,
      "end_time": 19503.0,
      "text": "So, imagine that you take a 19-hour, very long drive"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 19842.0,
      "end_time": 21162.0,
      "text": "to Disney World,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 21186.0,
      "end_time": 22690.0,
      "text": "with two kids in the back seat."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 24760.0,
      "end_time": 29208.0,
      "text": "And 15 minutes into this 19-hour trip,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 30351.0,
      "end_time": 33650.0,
      "text": "the immutable laws of nature dictate"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 33890.0,
      "end_time": 35144.0,
      "text": "that you get the question:"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 35169.0,
      "end_time": 36532.0,
      "text": "\"Are we there yet?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 36557.0,
      "end_time": 37814.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 38369.0,
      "end_time": 41826.0,
      "text": "So you answer this question a hundred more times, easily,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 41850.0,
      "end_time": 43900.0,
      "text": "in the negative,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 43330.0,
      "end_time": 44433.0,
      "text": "but you finally arrive."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 44457.0,
      "end_time": 47230.0,
      "text": "You have a wonderful, wonderful, wonderful trip."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 47254.0,
      "end_time": 52310.0,
      "text": "You drive 19 long hours back home."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 53358.0,
      "end_time": 54894.0,
      "text": "And when you get there,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 54919.0,
      "end_time": 56535.0,
      "text": "the police are waiting on you."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 57410.0,
      "end_time": 59428.0,
      "text": "They accuse you of committing a crime"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 59453.0,
      "end_time": 62720.0,
      "text": "that occurred while you were away in Florida."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 63684.0,
      "end_time": 66566.0,
      "text": "You tell anybody and everybody who will listen,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 66590.0,
      "end_time": 68530.0,
      "text": "\"I didn&#39;t do it!"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 68770.0,
      "end_time": 69428.0,
      "text": "I couldn&#39;t have done it!"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 70502.0,
      "end_time": 73289.0,
      "text": "I was hanging out with Mickey and Minnie and my kids!\""
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 74504.0,
      "end_time": 75823.0,
      "text": "But no one believes you."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 77104.0,
      "end_time": 78945.0,
      "text": "Ultimately, you&#39;re arrested,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 79624.0,
      "end_time": 80866.0,
      "text": "you&#39;re tried,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 80891.0,
      "end_time": 82191.0,
      "text": "you&#39;re convicted"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 82215.0,
      "end_time": 83508.0,
      "text": "and you are sentenced."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 84980.0,
      "end_time": 87102.0,
      "text": "And you spend 25 years in jail,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 88540.0,
      "end_time": 91432.0,
      "text": "until someone comes along and proves --"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 93384.0,
      "end_time": 94808.0,
      "text": "has the evidence to prove --"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 94832.0,
      "end_time": 98476.0,
      "text": "that you actually were in Florida"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 98500.0,
      "end_time": 100269.0,
      "text": "when this crime was committed."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 101626.0,
      "end_time": 102786.0,
      "text": "So."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 103651.0,
      "end_time": 105304.0,
      "text": "So, I&#39;m a Harvard Law professor,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 105329.0,
      "end_time": 109470.0,
      "text": "and the last several years, I have worked on"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 110105.0,
      "end_time": 112644.0,
      "text": "winning the release of innocent people"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 113193.0,
      "end_time": 115386.0,
      "text": "who&#39;ve been wrongfully convicted --"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 116410.0,
      "end_time": 117792.0,
      "text": "people like Jonathan Fleming,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 118582.0,
      "end_time": 121871.0,
      "text": "who spent 24 years, eight months in jail"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 121895.0,
      "end_time": 125493.0,
      "text": "for a murder that was committed in Brooklyn, New York,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 125517.0,
      "end_time": 129000.0,
      "text": "while he was in Disney World"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 129240.00000000001,
      "end_time": 130297.00000000001,
      "text": "with his kids."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 130966.00000000001,
      "end_time": 132116.0,
      "text": "How do we know this?"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 132702.0,
      "end_time": 134353.0,
      "text": "Because when he was arrested,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 135108.0,
      "end_time": 137899.0,
      "text": "among his property in his back pocket"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 138686.0,
      "end_time": 139927.0,
      "text": "was a receipt --"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 140865.0,
      "end_time": 142682.0,
      "text": "time-stamped receipt"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 142706.0,
      "end_time": 145566.0,
      "text": "that showed that he was in Disney World."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 146142.0,
      "end_time": 149267.0,
      "text": "That receipt was put in the police file,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 149291.0,
      "end_time": 151917.0,
      "text": "a copy of it was put in the prosecutor&#39;s file,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 151941.0,
      "end_time": 155173.0,
      "text": "and they never gave it to his public defender."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 155197.0,
      "end_time": 157139.0,
      "text": "In fact, nobody even knew it was there."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 157163.0,
      "end_time": 159902.0,
      "text": "It just sat there for 20-some-odd years."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 160746.0,
      "end_time": 164297.0,
      "text": "My team looked through the file, and we found it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 165227.0,
      "end_time": 166949.0,
      "text": "did the rest of the investigation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 166973.0,
      "end_time": 169260.0,
      "text": "and figured out someone else committed the crime."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 169284.0,
      "end_time": 172423.0,
      "text": "Mr. Fleming was in Disney World,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 172448.0,
      "end_time": 174387.0,
      "text": "and he is now released."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 174971.0,
      "end_time": 176923.0,
      "text": "Let me give you a little bit of context."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 177622.0,
      "end_time": 181760.0,
      "text": "So about three years ago, I got a call from the Brooklyn District Attorney."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 181784.0,
      "end_time": 185867.0,
      "text": "He asked whether I&#39;d be interested in designing a program"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 185891.0,
      "end_time": 187869.0,
      "text": "called a \"conviction review unit.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 187893.0,
      "end_time": 189174.0,
      "text": "So I said yes."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 189198.0,
      "end_time": 193865.0,
      "text": "A conviction review unit is essentially a unit in a prosecutor&#39;s office"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 193889.0,
      "end_time": 197600.0,
      "text": "where prosecutors look at their past cases"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 197300.0,
      "end_time": 199641.0,
      "text": "to determine whether or not they made mistakes."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 200285.0,
      "end_time": 202317.0,
      "text": "Over the course of the first year,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 202341.0,
      "end_time": 205435.0,
      "text": "we found about 13 wrongful convictions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 205459.0,
      "end_time": 207994.0,
      "text": "people having been in jail for decades,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 208180.0,
      "end_time": 209653.0,
      "text": "and we released all of them."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 209677.0,
      "end_time": 212355.0,
      "text": "It was the most in New York history."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 212379.0,
      "end_time": 213870.0,
      "text": "The program is still going on,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 213895.0,
      "end_time": 217162.0,
      "text": "and they&#39;re up to 21 releases now --"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 217186.0,
      "end_time": 221542.0,
      "text": "21 people who spent significant time behind bars."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 222770.0,
      "end_time": 227531.0,
      "text": "So let me tell you about a couple other of the men and women"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 227555.0,
      "end_time": 230839.0,
      "text": "that I interacted with in the course of this program."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 230863.0,
      "end_time": 233238.0,
      "text": "One name is Roger Logan."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 234190.0,
      "end_time": 237122.0,
      "text": "Mr. Logan had been in jail 17 years"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 237146.0,
      "end_time": 238625.0,
      "text": "and wrote me a letter."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 238650.0,
      "end_time": 240793.0,
      "text": "It was a simple letter; it basically said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 240817.0,
      "end_time": 243871.0,
      "text": "\"Professor Sullivan, I&#39;m innocent. I&#39;ve been framed."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 243895.0,
      "end_time": 245250.0,
      "text": "Can you look at my case?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 246990.0,
      "end_time": 249243.0,
      "text": "At first blush, the case seemed like it was open and shut,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 249267.0,
      "end_time": 251299.0,
      "text": "but my research had shown"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 252312.0,
      "end_time": 254935.0,
      "text": "that single-witness identification cases"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 254959.0,
      "end_time": 256237.0,
      "text": "are prone to error."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 257197.0,
      "end_time": 258995.0,
      "text": "It doesn&#39;t mean he was innocent,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 259190.0,
      "end_time": 262337.0,
      "text": "it just means we ought to look a little bit closer at those cases."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 262361.0,
      "end_time": 263671.0,
      "text": "So we did."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 263695.0,
      "end_time": 265695.0,
      "text": "And the facts were relatively simple."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 265720.0,
      "end_time": 268802.0,
      "text": "The eyewitness said she heard a shot,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 268826.0,
      "end_time": 271877.0,
      "text": "and she ran to the next building and turned around and looked,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 271901.0,
      "end_time": 273482.0,
      "text": "and there was Mr. Logan."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 274252.0,
      "end_time": 278536.0,
      "text": "And he was tried and convicted and in jail for 17-some-odd years."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 278560.0,
      "end_time": 281374.0,
      "text": "But it was a single-witness case, so we took a look at it."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 281398.0,
      "end_time": 284518.0,
      "text": "I sent some people to the scene, and there was an inconsistency."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 284542.0,
      "end_time": 289679.0,
      "text": "And to put it politely:"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 289703.0,
      "end_time": 293361.0,
      "text": "Usain Bolt couldn&#39;t have run from where she said she was"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 293386.0,
      "end_time": 294574.0,
      "text": "to the other spot."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 294598.0,
      "end_time": 295750.0,
      "text": "Right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 295774.0,
      "end_time": 298191.0,
      "text": "So we knew that wasn&#39;t true."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 298745.0,
      "end_time": 300842.0,
      "text": "So it still didn&#39;t mean that he didn&#39;t do it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 300866.0,
      "end_time": 304849.0,
      "text": "but we knew something was maybe fishy about this witness."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 305454.0,
      "end_time": 307488.0,
      "text": "So we looked through the file,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 307512.0,
      "end_time": 309851.0,
      "text": "a piece of paper in the file had a number on it."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 309875.0,
      "end_time": 312841.0,
      "text": "The number indicated that this witness had a record."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 312865.0,
      "end_time": 316673.0,
      "text": "We went back through 20 years of non-digitized papers"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 316697.0,
      "end_time": 319273.0,
      "text": "to figure out what this record was about,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 319297.0,
      "end_time": 321784.0,
      "text": "and it turned out -- it turned out --"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 321808.0,
      "end_time": 325316.0,
      "text": "the eyewitness was in jail"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 325340.0,
      "end_time": 327258.0,
      "text": "when she said she saw what she saw."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 329538.0,
      "end_time": 331751.0,
      "text": "The man spent 17 years behind bars."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 333296.0,
      "end_time": 338630.0,
      "text": "The last one is a case about two boys,"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 338870.0,
      "end_time": 339908.0,
      "text": "Willie Stuckey, David McCallum."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 340822.0,
      "end_time": 342407.0,
      "text": "They were arrested at 15,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 343140.0,
      "end_time": 347340.0,
      "text": "and their conviction was vacated 29 years later."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 348685.0,
      "end_time": 350479.0,
      "text": "Now this was a case,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 350503.0,
      "end_time": 353306.0,
      "text": "once again -- first blush, it looked open and shut."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 353331.0,
      "end_time": 354603.0,
      "text": "They had confessed."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 355570.0,
      "end_time": 358320.0,
      "text": "But my research showed that juvenile confessions"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 358345.0,
      "end_time": 359834.0,
      "text": "without a parent present"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 359858.0,
      "end_time": 361293.0,
      "text": "are prone to error."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 361317.0,
      "end_time": 363583.0,
      "text": "The DNA cases proved this several times."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 363607.0,
      "end_time": 364981.0,
      "text": "So we took a close look."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 365528.0,
      "end_time": 367377.0,
      "text": "We looked at the confession,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 367401.0,
      "end_time": 368565.0,
      "text": "and it turned out,"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 368589.0,
      "end_time": 370451.0,
      "text": "there was something in the confession"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 370475.0,
      "end_time": 372443.0,
      "text": "that those boys could not have known."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 372467.0,
      "end_time": 375198.0,
      "text": "The only people who knew it were police and prosecutors."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 375222.0,
      "end_time": 377493.0,
      "text": "We knew what really happened;"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 377517.0,
      "end_time": 379760.0,
      "text": "someone told them to say this."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 379100.0,
      "end_time": 380969.0,
      "text": "We don&#39;t exactly know who,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 380993.0,
      "end_time": 382460.0,
      "text": "which person did,"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 382484.0,
      "end_time": 385378.0,
      "text": "but any rate, the confession was coerced,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 385403.0,
      "end_time": 386757.0,
      "text": "we determined."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 387242.0,
      "end_time": 389740.0,
      "text": "We then went back and did forensics"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 389980.0,
      "end_time": 390784.0,
      "text": "and did a fulsome investigation"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 390808.0,
      "end_time": 392204.0,
      "text": "and found that two other,"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 392228.0,
      "end_time": 395870.0,
      "text": "much older, different heights, different hairstyle,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 395111.0,
      "end_time": 397445.0,
      "text": "two other people committed the crime,"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 397469.0,
      "end_time": 398739.0,
      "text": "not these two boys."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 399161.0,
      "end_time": 401206.0,
      "text": "I actually went to court that day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 401230.0,
      "end_time": 404772.0,
      "text": "for what&#39;s called a \"vacatur hearing,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 404796.0,
      "end_time": 406907.0,
      "text": "where the conviction is thrown out."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 406931.0,
      "end_time": 408633.0,
      "text": "I went to court; I wanted to see"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 409281.0,
      "end_time": 411788.0,
      "text": "Mr. McCallum walk out of there."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 411812.0,
      "end_time": 412966.0,
      "text": "So I went to court,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 412990.0,
      "end_time": 415759.0,
      "text": "and the judge said something that judges say all the time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 415783.0,
      "end_time": 417992.0,
      "text": "but this took on a really special meaning."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 418513.0,
      "end_time": 421133.0,
      "text": "He looked up after the arguments and said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 421157.0,
      "end_time": 422359.0,
      "text": "\"Mr. McCallum,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 422928.0,
      "end_time": 424817.0,
      "text": "he said five beautiful words:"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 425414.0,
      "end_time": 428865.0,
      "text": "\"You are free to go.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 430359.0,
      "end_time": 431972.0,
      "text": "Can you imagine?"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 431997.0,
      "end_time": 434375.0,
      "text": "After just about 30 years:"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 435135.0,
      "end_time": 436664.0,
      "text": "\"You are free to go.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 438545.0,
      "end_time": 440324.0,
      "text": "And he walked out of that courtroom."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 441415.0,
      "end_time": 444594.0,
      "text": "Unfortunately, his codefendant, Mr. Stuckey,"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 444619.0,
      "end_time": 446748.0,
      "text": "didn&#39;t get the benefit of that."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 447297.0,
      "end_time": 449155.0,
      "text": "You see, Mr. Stuckey died in prison"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 450000.0,
      "end_time": 452880.0,
      "text": "at 34 years old,"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 452112.0,
      "end_time": 455504.0,
      "text": "and his mother sat at counsel table in his place."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 456718.0,
      "end_time": 459276.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ll never forget this the rest of my life."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 459300.0,
      "end_time": 462277.0,
      "text": "She just rocked at the table, saying,"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 462301.0,
      "end_time": 464260.0,
      "text": "\"I knew my baby didn&#39;t do this."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 464285.0,
      "end_time": 466504.0,
      "text": "I knew my baby didn&#39;t do this.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 466528.0,
      "end_time": 467911.0,
      "text": "And her baby didn&#39;t do this."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 468633.0,
      "end_time": 469871.0,
      "text": "Two other guys did it."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 470937.0,
      "end_time": 474223.0,
      "text": "If there&#39;s anything that we&#39;ve learned, anything that I&#39;ve learned,"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 474247.0,
      "end_time": 477435.0,
      "text": "with this conviction integrity work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 477459.0,
      "end_time": 480398.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s that justice doesn&#39;t happen."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 481599.0,
      "end_time": 485428.0,
      "text": "People make justice happen."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 488261.0,
      "end_time": 492156.0,
      "text": "Justice is not a thing that just descends from above"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 492180.0,
      "end_time": 493560.0,
      "text": "and makes everything right."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 494422.0,
      "end_time": 498405.0,
      "text": "If it did, Mr. Stuckey wouldn&#39;t have died in prison."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 499576.0,
      "end_time": 501299.0,
      "text": "Justice is something"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 501323.0,
      "end_time": 504421.0,
      "text": "that people of goodwill make happen."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 505705.0,
      "end_time": 509300.0,
      "text": "Justice is a decision."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 512212.0,
      "end_time": 513939.0,
      "text": "Justice is a decision."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 515280.0,
      "end_time": 517621.0,
      "text": "We make justice happen."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 518126.0,
      "end_time": 520440.0,
      "text": "You know, the scary thing is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 520679.99999999994,
      "end_time": 522684.99999999994,
      "text": "in each of these three cases I described,"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 522710.00000000006,
      "end_time": 525312.0,
      "text": "it would have only taken just an extra minute --"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 525336.0,
      "end_time": 526951.0,
      "text": "an extra minute --"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 526975.0,
      "end_time": 529118.0,
      "text": "for someone to look through the file"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 529142.0,
      "end_time": 530630.0,
      "text": "and find this receipt."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 531624.0,
      "end_time": 534680.0,
      "text": "Just one -- to look through the file, find the receipt,"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 535504.0,
      "end_time": 537371.0,
      "text": "give it to the public defender."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 538702.0,
      "end_time": 541244.0,
      "text": "It would have taken someone just a minute"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 541268.0,
      "end_time": 545915.0,
      "text": "to look at the video confession and say, \"That cannot be.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 546999.0,
      "end_time": 548285.0,
      "text": "Just a minute."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 549524.0,
      "end_time": 552504.0,
      "text": "And perhaps Mr. Stuckey would be alive today."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 553271.0,
      "end_time": 556651.0,
      "text": "It reminds me of one of my favorite poems."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 556676.0,
      "end_time": 560959.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a poem that Benjamin Elijah Mays would always recite,"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 560983.0,
      "end_time": 562695.0,
      "text": "and he called it \"God&#39;s Minute.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 562720.0,
      "end_time": 564293.0,
      "text": "And it goes something like this:"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 564317.0,
      "end_time": 566434.0,
      "text": "\"I have only just a minute,"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 566458.0,
      "end_time": 568485.0,
      "text": "only 60 seconds in it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 568509.0,
      "end_time": 570784.0,
      "text": "forced upon me, can&#39;t refuse it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 570808.0,
      "end_time": 573740.0,
      "text": "didn&#39;t seek it, didn&#39;t choose it."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 573980.0,
      "end_time": 574651.0,
      "text": "But it&#39;s up to me to use it."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 574676.0,
      "end_time": 578114.0,
      "text": "I must suffer if I lose it, give account if I abuse it."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 578995.0,
      "end_time": 581249.0,
      "text": "Just a tiny little minute,"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 581925.0,
      "end_time": 584405.0,
      "text": "but eternity is in it.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 585723.0,
      "end_time": 587272.0,
      "text": "If I were to charge"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 587297.0,
      "end_time": 588930.0,
      "text": "each and every one of us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 589754.0,
      "end_time": 592163.0,
      "text": "I would want to say something like,"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 593782.0,
      "end_time": 594934.0,
      "text": "\"Every day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 595688.0,
      "end_time": 596839.0,
      "text": "every day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 597755.0,
      "end_time": 599819.0,
      "text": "take just one extra minute"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 601620.0,
      "end_time": 602996.0,
      "text": "and do some justice."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 604752.0,
      "end_time": 606154.0,
      "text": "You don&#39;t have to --"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 606178.0,
      "end_time": 610191.0,
      "text": "I mean, some people spend their careers and their lives,"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 610215.0,
      "end_time": 611453.0,
      "text": "like public defenders,"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 611477.0,
      "end_time": 612717.0,
      "text": "doing justice every day."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 614260.0,
      "end_time": 616346.0,
      "text": "But in your professional lives, whatever you do,"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 616370.0,
      "end_time": 618600.0,
      "text": "take time out"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 618840.0,
      "end_time": 619247.0,
      "text": "to just"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 620396.0,
      "end_time": 621683.0,
      "text": "do some justice."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 621707.0,
      "end_time": 623421.0,
      "text": "Make a colleague feel better."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 623903.0,
      "end_time": 626454.0,
      "text": "If you hear something that&#39;s sexist,"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 627208.0,
      "end_time": 629365.0,
      "text": "don&#39;t laugh, speak up."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 630217.0,
      "end_time": 632537.0,
      "text": "If someone is down, lift them up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 632561.0,
      "end_time": 635255.0,
      "text": "one extra minute each day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 636730.0,
      "end_time": 638395.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;ll be a great, great place."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 638419.0,
      "end_time": 640215.0,
      "text": "I want to show you something."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 641777.0,
      "end_time": 644752.0,
      "text": "Now, above me is a picture"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 644776.0,
      "end_time": 646197.0,
      "text": "of David McCallum."
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 647173.0,
      "end_time": 650530.0,
      "text": "This is the day he was released from prison."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 650770.0,
      "end_time": 653134.0,
      "text": "After 30 years, he got to hug a niece"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 653158.0,
      "end_time": 655950.0,
      "text": "he had never been able to touch before."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 657198.0,
      "end_time": 658555.0,
      "text": "And I asked him then,"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 659383.0,
      "end_time": 662820.0,
      "text": "I said, \"What&#39;s the first thing you want to do?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 662106.0,
      "end_time": 664485.0,
      "text": "And he said, \"I just want to walk on the sidewalk"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 664509.0,
      "end_time": 666690.0,
      "text": "without anybody telling me where to go.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 667290.0,
      "end_time": 668995.0,
      "text": "Wasn&#39;t bitter,"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 669190.0,
      "end_time": 670925.0,
      "text": "just wanted to walk on the sidewalk."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 671655.0,
      "end_time": 674661.0,
      "text": "I spoke to Mr. McCallum about two weeks ago."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 675189.0,
      "end_time": 676363.0,
      "text": "I went to New York."
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 676387.0,
      "end_time": 679150.0,
      "text": "It was on the two-year anniversary"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 679174.0,
      "end_time": 680744.0,
      "text": "of his release."
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 681100.0,
      "end_time": 682740.0,
      "text": "And we talked,"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 682764.0,
      "end_time": 685228.0,
      "text": "we laughed, we hugged, we cried."
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 685855.0,
      "end_time": 688600.0,
      "text": "And he&#39;s doing quite well."
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 688840.0,
      "end_time": 691969.0,
      "text": "And one of the things he said when we met with him"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 691994.0,
      "end_time": 695124.0,
      "text": "is that he now has dedicated his life"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 695148.0,
      "end_time": 696517.0,
      "text": "and his career"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 696541.0,
      "end_time": 700700.0,
      "text": "to ensuring that nobody else is locked up unjustly."
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 701771.0,
      "end_time": 703772.0,
      "text": "Justice, my friends,"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 705416.0,
      "end_time": 706665.0,
      "text": "is a decision."
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 707346.0,
      "end_time": 708553.0,
      "text": "Thank you very much."
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 708577.0,
      "end_time": 712717.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}